<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">後</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うしろ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>から<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">欺</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">だま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>し<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">討</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">う</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ちに×<span rend="superscript" rendition="sup">（２）</span>り<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">倒</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">たお</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>された<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">君</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>たちの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">血</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>はべっとりと<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">廊下</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ろうか</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">染</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">そ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>め<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">君</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>たちの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">唇</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くちびる</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">最後</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さいご</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>まで<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">反戦</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はんせん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">叫</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さけ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>び<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">続</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">つゞ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>けた<lb />
<lb />
よし<lb />
たけり<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">立</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">た</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>って<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">兵士</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">へいし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>らを<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">宥</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">なだ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>めかねてやつらのひとりが<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">自殺</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">じさつ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>せうと、よし<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">泥</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">どろ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>のやうに<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">酔</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">よ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>っ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">払</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ぱら</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>はせた<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">兵士</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">へいし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>らを<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">御用船</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ごようせん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>へ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">積</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">つ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>み込んで<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">送</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おく</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>り<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">出</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">だ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>さうと<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">廊下</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ろうか</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">沁</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">し</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>み込んだ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">君</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>たちの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">血</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は<lb />
それで<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">拭</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ぬぐ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>はれたか<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">溢</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あふ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>れ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">出</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">で</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>る<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">血</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>どろと<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">共</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">とも</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">口</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">衝</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">つ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>いて<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">迸</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ほとば</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>しった<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">君</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>たちの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">叫</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さけ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>びは<lb />
それで<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">消</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">け</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>されたか<lb />
<lb />
おゝ今<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">消燈喇叭</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">せうとうらっぱ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">夜風</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">よかぜ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">衝</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">つ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>いて<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">響</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ひび</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>き<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">渡</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">わた</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>り<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">窓</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">まど</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>はひとつひとつ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">闇</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">やみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">溶</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">と</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>けて<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">行</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ゆ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>く<lb />
おれは<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">伸</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">の</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>び<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">上</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あが</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>り<lb />
かじかんだ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">手</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">て</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">挙</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>げて<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">仲間</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">なかま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">合図</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あいず</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>をする<lb />
そして<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">俺達</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おれたち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">立上</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">たちあが</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span rend="notes">［＃ルビの「たちあが」は底本では「たちあ」］</span>りマントを<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">捨</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">す</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>て<lb />
すばやく<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">塀</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">へい</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">乗</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">の</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>り<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">越</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>えて<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">突進</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">とっしん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>する<lb />
<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">俺達</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おれたち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">手</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">て</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>にはビラがあり<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">俺達</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おれたち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>のポケットにはドスがある<lb />
ビラは<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">眠</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ねむ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>った<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">営舎</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">えいしゃ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">揺</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ゆ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>り<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">覚</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>まし<lb />
ドスは<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">倒</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">たふ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>された<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">同志</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">どうし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">血</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">洗</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あら</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ふだらう<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">風</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かぜ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>よ<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">兵営</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">へいえい</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">隅々</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">すみずみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>までこのビラを<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">蒔</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>き<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">散</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>らせ！<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">塀</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">へい</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>よ<lb />
「兵士委員会を作れ！」<lb />
の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">叫</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さけ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>びを<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">営庭</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">えいてい</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>一ぱいに<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">跳</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">は</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ね<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">返</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かえ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>せ！<lb />
